OL,5, Security minister and Tory MP Tom      
OL,6, Tugendhat has been banned from driving 
OL,7, for six months after he was caught     
OL,8, driving with his mobile phone in his   
OL,9, hand.                                  
OL,11,FThe MP for Tonbridge and Malling, who  
OL,12,Flives in Clapham, was caught driving   
OL,13,Fwith the device in London on 14 April. 
OL,15,FJudge Jack McGarva said at Westminster 
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court: "Using a mobile    
OL,17,Fphone in any way is a distraction.     
OL,19,F"Without any doubt it impairs people's 
OL,20,Fability to drive."                     
